OL,3,CPolice watchdog to publish findings on
OL,4,Ctriple killer despite 'gagging' claims
OL,6,FA watchdog has insisted it will
OL,7,Fpublish its findings into police
OL,8,Fdealings with Nottingham triple killer
OL,9,FValdo Calocane - despite claims that
OL,10,Fvictims' families were "gagged" from
OL,11,Fspeaking out about it.
OL,13,FThe Independent Office for Police
OL,14,FConduct is investigating the way
OL,15,FLeicestershire Police officers dealt
OL,16,Fwith alleged assaults by Calocane, a
OL,17,Fmonth before the Nottingham attacks in
OL,18,FJune 2023.
