OL,3,CPolice watchdog to publish findings on
OL,4,Ctriple killer despite 'gagging' claims
OL,6,FBut Emma Webber, the mother of Barnaby
OL,7,FWebber, said she and other families
OL,8,Fwere forced into a non-disclosure
OL,9,Fagreement (NDA), preventing them
OL,10,Fspeaking about the investigation.
OL,12,FCalocane, who had been diagnosed with
OL,13,Fparanoid schizophrenia, was sentenced
OL,14,Fto an indefinite hospital order after
OL,15,Fkilling 19-year-old students Barnaby
OL,16,Fand Grace O'Malley Kumar and caretaker
OL,17,FIan Coates, 65. He tried to kill three
OL,18,Fothers in a spate of attacks.
