OL,3,CPolice watchdog to publish findings on
OL,4,Ctriple killer despite 'gagging' claims
OL,6,FThe IOPC previously said two
OL,7,Fconstables and a sergeant were being
OL,8,Finvestigated.
OL,10,FIt is claimed Calocane assaulted two
OL,11,Fcolleagues at an industrial estate in
OL,12,FKegworth, Leicester, in May 2023.
OL,14,FMrs Webber said she called on the IOPC
OL,15,Fto "do the right thing" and urged them
OL,16,Fto make the findings public "so that
OL,17,Ffull scrutiny can take place".
