OL,3,CPolice watchdog to publish findings on
OL,4,Ctriple killer despite 'gagging' claims
OL,6,FThe watchdog said a confidentiality
OL,7,Fagreement was "needed" in order to
OL,8,Fshare the report with the victims'
OL,9,Ffamilies at the earliest opportunity.
OL,11,FThe IOPC said it anticipated being
OL,12,Fable to publish the findings and
OL,13,Foutcomes of the investigation "in the
OL,14,Fcoming weeks".
OL,16,FIt follows NHS England's decision to
OL,17,Fpublish the full report into the
OL,18,Fmental health care received by
OL,19,FCalocane prior to the attacks, after
OL,20,Finitially intending to only publish a
OL,21,Fsummary.
