OL,4,Ctriple killer despite 'gagging' claims
OL,6,FMrs Webber said: "We were forced to
OL,7,Fsign NDA's by NHSE to promise that we
OL,8,Fwould not disclose their investigation
OL,9,Finto Calocane's care.
OL,11,F"Under pressure from us, they were
OL,12,Fforced to U-turn and disclose the
OL,13,Freport in full themselves.
OL,15,F"As (Health Secretary) Wes Streeting
OL,16,Fhimself said, sunlight is the best
OL,17,Fdisinfectant ` the same principle
OL,18,Fapplies to the IOPC investigations
OL,19,Finto the numerous police failings in
OL,20,Four case."
