OL,3,CPolice watchdog to publish findings on
OL,4,Ctriple killer despite 'gagging' claims
OL,6,FShe continued: "Like the NHS, the IOPC
OL,7,Fhave also sought to gag us from
OL,8,Fspeaking publicly and have forced us
OL,9,Fto sign NDAs saying we will not reveal
OL,10,Ftheir reports and findings.
OL,12,F"I now call on the IOPC to do the
OL,13,Fright thing like the NHS did and
OL,14,Fdisclose their reports to the public
OL,15,Fso that full scrutiny can take place.
OL,17,F"It is the only way that real lessons
OL,18,Fare going to be learned and lasting
OL,19,Fchange put in place so that no other
OL,20,Ffamily should have to endure the
OL,21,Ftorture that we are."
OL,26,@nD@POUtD@AOUyD@AOU}D@UO]
