OL,4,Ctriple killer despite 'gagging' claims
OL,6,FRadd Seiger, an adviser to the
OL,7,Fvictims' families, said the IOPC's
OL,8,Fdecision to impose an NDA was
OL,9,F"inexcusable".
OL,11,FHe said: "It is inexcusable for any
OL,12,Fwatchdog to seek to gag families of
OL,13,Fvictims of serious crimes in this
OL,14,Fmanner.
OL,16,F"That practice must be stopped."
