OL,6,FIOPC director Derrick Campbell said:
OL,7,F"We completed an investigation into
OL,8,FLeicestershire Police contact with
OL,9,FValdo Calocane prior to the killings
OL,10,Fand in particular the actions and
OL,11,Fdecisions of officers investigating
OL,12,Falleged assaults by him.
OL,14,F"In order to share our report and
OL,15,Funderlying evidence with the families
OL,16,Fof his victims at the earliest
OL,17,Fopportunity, a confidentiality
OL,18,Fagreement was needed.
OL,26,@oD@AOUvD@AOU
